<section class="content-page" id="challenge-review-page">
  <div class="align-container">
    <p class="section-label">Challenge Review</p>
    <h1>Request a Challenge Review</h1>
    <p>
      Turning a proof into a formal challenge requires verifying deadlines, standing, and
      documentation. Complete the intake below so we can confirm your case and outline the next
      steps.
    </p>

    <div class="action-step">
      <h2 class="step-title"><span class="step-number">1</span>What you can expect</h2>
      <p class="step-description">
        You will receive a written review that confirms jurisdiction, cites the controlling bylaws,
        and outlines a recommended filing path.
      </p>
    </div>

    <ul class="action-list">
      <li>Standing and jurisdiction analysis grounded in WV Democratic Party and DNC rules</li>
      <li>Deadline timeline with citations to the applicable bylaws or charter</li>
      <li>Evidence and documentation checklist tailored to your challenge</li>
      <li>Optional support plan if you qualify for end-to-end filing assistance</li>
    </ul>

    <div class="action-step">
      <h2 class="step-title"><span class="step-number">2</span>Gather essential details</h2>
      <p class="step-description">
        Share what happened, when it occurred, and the proof you have so we can confirm the 30-day
        clock and the proper venue.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="pre-check-box">
      <h2>Details to include</h2>
      <p>Having this information ready keeps the review fast and focused:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor">
            <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 1 0 0-16 8 8 0 0 0 0 16Zm3.857-9.809a.75.75 0 0 0-1.214-.882l-3.483 4.79-1.88-1.88a.75.75 0 1 0-1.06 1.061l2.5 2.5a.75.75 0 0 0 1.137-.089l4-5.5Z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
          </svg>
          <span
            >The committee, officer, or body you're contesting and the date of the decision or
            meeting.</span
          >
        </li>
        <li>
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor">
            <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 1 0 0-16 8 8 0 0 0 0 16Zm3.857-9.809a.75.75 0 0 0-1.214-.882l-3.483 4.79-1.88-1.88a.75.75 0 1 0-1.06 1.061l2.5 2.5a.75.75 0 0 0 1.137-.089l4-5.5Z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
          </svg>
          <span
            >What steps you've already taken with the West Virginia Democratic Party to seek a
            remedy.</span
          >
        </li>
        <li>
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor">
            <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 1 0 0-16 8 8 0 0 0 0 16Zm3.857-9.809a.75.75 0 0 0-1.214-.882l-3.483 4.79-1.88-1.88a.75.75 0 1 0-1.06 1.061l2.5 2.5a.75.75 0 0 0 1.137-.089l4-5.5Z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
          </svg>
          <span
            >Links to Democratic Justice proofs, documents, or recordings that back up your claim.</span
          >
        </li>
        <li>
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor">
            <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 1 0 0-16 8 8 0 0 0 0 16Zm3.857-9.809a.75.75 0 0 0-1.214-.882l-3.483 4.79-1.88-1.88a.75.75 0 1 0-1.06 1.061l2.5 2.5a.75.75 0 0 0 1.137-.089l4-5.5Z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
          </svg>
          <span>The remedy you want ordered—rehearing, new vote, rule change, or another fix.</span>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <hr class="section-divider">

    <h2 id="review-form">Challenge Review Intake Form</h2>
    <p>
      We respond within two business days. If a filing deadline is under five days away, mention it
      so we can prioritize your review.
    </p>

    <form
      id="secure-contact"
      name="challenge-review"
      method="POST"
      netlify
      netlify-honeypot="bot-field"
      class="cta-form multi-step-form"
      aria-labelledby="review-form"
      data-form-id="challenge-review"
      data-success-target="#challenge-review-success"
    >
      <input type="hidden" name="form-name" value="challenge-review">
      <p class="visually-hidden">
        <label>Leave this empty <input name="bot-field"></label>
      </p>

      <ol class="form-progress" aria-hidden="true">
        <li class="is-active" data-progress-step>Contact</li>
        <li data-progress-step>Deadline</li>
        <li data-progress-step>Details</li>
        <li data-progress-step>Relief</li>
      </ol>
      <p class="form-progress__status" data-progress-status aria-live="polite">Step 1 of 4</p>

      <fieldset data-form-step>
        <legend>Step 1 of 4: Your information</legend>

        <div class="form-group">
          <label for="full-name">Full name</label>
          <p class="form-help" id="full-name-help">
            We will address the written review to this name.
          </p>
          <input
            type="text"
            id="full-name"
            name="full-name"
            placeholder="Jane Doe"
            aria-describedby="full-name-help"
            required
          >
        </div>

        <div class="form-group">
          <label for="email">Email address</label>
          <p class="form-help" id="email-help">
            We'll send confirmation and follow up questions to this inbox.
          </p>
          <input
            type="email"
            id="email"
            name="email"
            placeholder="your@email.com"
            aria-describedby="email-help"
            required
          >
        </div>

        <div class="form-group">
          <label for="phone">Phone (optional)</label>
          <p class="form-help" id="phone-help">
            Share a mobile number if you'd like a text update when we respond.
          </p>
          <input
            type="tel"
            id="phone"
            name="phone"
            placeholder="304-555-0123"
            aria-describedby="phone-help"
          >
        </div>

        <div class="form-group">
          <label for="county">County or local organization</label>
          <p class="form-help" id="county-help">
            List the county committee or local group connected to your challenge.
          </p>
          <input
            type="text"
            id="county"
            name="county"
            placeholder="County, committee, or group involved"
            aria-describedby="county-help"
          >
        </div>

        <div class="form-group">
          <span class="form-label" id="registration-label"
            >Are you registered to vote as a Democrat in West Virginia?</span
          >
          <p class="form-help" id="registration-help">
            The WVSDEC can only accept filings from registered West Virginia Democrats or qualified
            representatives.
          </p>
          <div
            class="form-options"
            role="group"
            aria-labelledby="registration-label"
            aria-describedby="registration-help"
          >
            <label class="form-option">
              <input type="radio" name="wv-registered" value="yes" required>
              <span>Yes — I'm a registered West Virginia Democrat</span>
            </label>
            <label class="form-option">
              <input type="radio" name="wv-registered" value="no">
              <span>No — I'm assisting someone else or contesting as another entity</span>
            </label>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="form-group" id="registration-explanation" data-registration-explanation hidden>
          <label for="registration-notes">Explain your connection to the party</label>
          <p class="form-help" id="registration-notes-help">
            If you're filing on behalf of someone else or a committee, tell us how the case meets
            the standing requirement.
          </p>
          <textarea
            id="registration-notes"
            name="registration-notes"
            rows="3"
            placeholder="Share how you or the person you represent meets the WVSDEC eligibility rules."
            aria-describedby="registration-notes-help"
          ></textarea>
        </div>
      </fieldset>

      <fieldset data-form-step hidden>
        <legend>Step 2 of 4: Confirm the deadline</legend>

        <div class="form-group">
          <label for="decision-date">When did the decision or event happen?</label>
          <p class="form-help" id="decision-date-help">
            Use the meeting, vote, or decision date so we can verify the 30-day filing window.
          </p>
          <input
            type="date"
            id="decision-date"
            name="decision-date"
            aria-describedby="decision-date-help"
            required
          >
        </div>

        <p class="form-alert" data-date-warning role="status" aria-live="polite" hidden></p>

        <div class="form-group" id="deadline-notes-group" data-deadline-notes hidden>
          <label for="deadline-notes">Explain any timing concerns</label>
          <p class="form-help" id="deadline-notes-help">
            If it has been more than 30 days, tell us about tolling arguments, new evidence, or
            ongoing violations.
          </p>
          <textarea
            id="deadline-notes"
            name="deadline-notes"
            rows="3"
            placeholder="Describe why the case should still be heard or note any continuing violations."
            aria-describedby="deadline-notes-help"
          ></textarea>
        </div>

        <div class="form-group">
          <label for="decision-maker">Which committee, officer, or body was involved?</label>
          <p class="form-help" id="decision-maker-help">
            List the exact committee, officer, or body whose action you're challenging.
          </p>
          <input
            type="text"
            id="decision-maker"
            name="decision-maker"
            placeholder="e.g., Kanawha County Democratic Executive Committee"
            aria-describedby="decision-maker-help"
            required
          >
        </div>
      </fieldset>

      <fieldset data-form-step hidden>
        <legend>Step 3 of 4: Describe what happened</legend>

        <div class="form-group">
          <label for="challenge-type">Which process are you pursuing?</label>
          <p class="form-help" id="challenge-type-help">
            We'll match your facts to the correct section of the bylaws.
          </p>
          <select
            id="challenge-type"
            name="challenge-type"
            aria-describedby="challenge-type-help"
            required
          >
            <option value="" disabled selected>Select an option</option>
            <option value="Appeal a decision">Appeal a decision</option>
            <option value="Contest a delegation">Contest a delegation</option>
            <option value="Remove a member for cause">Remove a member for cause</option>
            <option value="Remove an officer">Remove an officer</option>
            <option value="DNC Credentials Challenge">DNC Credentials Challenge</option>
            <option value="DNC Rules Complaint">DNC Rules Complaint</option>
            <option value="Not sure yet">Not sure yet</option>
          </select>
        </div>

        <div class="form-group">
          <label for="summary">Provide a brief description of your claim</label>
          <p class="form-help" id="summary-help">
            Summarize the rule violation, timeline, and who was affected.
          </p>
          <textarea
            id="summary"
            name="summary"
            rows="4"
            placeholder="Provide a brief description of your claim, including key facts and dates."
            aria-describedby="summary-help"
            required
          ></textarea>
        </div>

        <div class="form-group">
          <label for="proof-links">Supporting links or documents (optional)</label>
          <p class="form-help" id="proof-links-help">
            Share Democratic Justice proof links, recordings, or describe documents we should
            review.
          </p>
          <textarea
            id="proof-links"
            name="proof-links"
            rows="3"
            placeholder="Paste proof links, cite recordings, or note documents you can share."
            aria-describedby="proof-links-help"
          ></textarea>
        </div>
      </fieldset>

      <fieldset data-form-step hidden>
        <legend>Step 4 of 4: Prior remedies and relief</legend>

        <div class="form-group">
          <span class="form-label" id="prior-remedy-label"
            >Have you already asked the WV Democratic Party for relief?</span
          >
          <p class="form-help" id="prior-remedy-help">
            Tell us about grievances, appeals, or informal outreach you've attempted.
          </p>
          <div
            class="form-options"
            role="group"
            aria-labelledby="prior-remedy-label"
            aria-describedby="prior-remedy-help"
          >
            <label class="form-option">
              <input type="radio" name="prior-remedy" value="yes" required>
              <span>Yes — I've already requested relief</span>
            </label>
            <label class="form-option">
              <input type="radio" name="prior-remedy" value="no">
              <span>No — this is my first request</span>
            </label>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="form-group" data-prior-remedy="yes" hidden>
          <label for="state-steps">Describe the steps you've taken so far</label>
          <p class="form-help" id="state-steps-help">
            Include who you contacted, meeting dates, and any responses received.
          </p>
          <textarea
            id="state-steps"
            name="state-steps"
            rows="3"
            placeholder="Share who you contacted, when you met, and how they responded."
            aria-describedby="state-steps-help"
          ></textarea>
        </div>

        <div class="form-group" data-prior-remedy="no" hidden>
          <label for="prior-barriers">Tell us what has stopped you from seeking relief</label>
          <p class="form-help" id="prior-barriers-help">
            Knowing obstacles helps us recommend the next procedural step.
          </p>
          <textarea
            id="prior-barriers"
            name="prior-barriers"
            rows="3"
            placeholder="Explain any barriers to filing or why you're seeking our help first."
            aria-describedby="prior-barriers-help"
          ></textarea>
        </div>

        <div class="form-group">
          <label for="remedy">What remedy or support are you seeking?</label>
          <p class="form-help" id="remedy-help">
            Describe the outcome you want—such as a rehearing, new vote, or policy change.
          </p>
          <textarea
            id="remedy"
            name="remedy"
            rows="3"
            placeholder="Tell us the remedy you're requesting and how we can support you."
            aria-describedby="remedy-help"
            required
          ></textarea>
        </div>
      </fieldset>

      <div class="form-navigation" data-form-navigation>
        <button type="button" class="btn-secondary" data-form-prev disabled>Back</button>
        <button type="button" data-form-next>Next Step</button>
        <button type="submit" data-form-submit hidden>Submit Review Request</button>
      </div>
    </form>

    <div
      id="challenge-review-success"
      class="form-success"
      role="status"
      aria-live="polite"
      tabindex="-1"
      hidden
    >
      <h3>Thanks—your review request is in our queue.</h3>
      <p>
        We received your challenge review intake and will reply within two business days. If you
        flagged an urgent deadline, we'll prioritize your case and follow up as quickly as possible.
      </p>
    </div>

    <p id="cta-error" role="alert">
      Sorry—something went wrong. Email
      <a href="mailto:setho@democraticjustice.org">setho@democraticjustice.org</a>.
    </p>

    <p style="font-size:13px;margin-top:16px;opacity:.9">
      We keep every intake confidential. If the form gives you trouble, email
      <a href="mailto:setho@democraticjustice.org">setho@democraticjustice.org</a> with "Challenge
      Review" in the subject.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>
